author: scheu
msg: Contributor: Mike Rheinheimer and Sam Isokpunwu
Changes are made to the JAX-WS AsyncResponse to use the client's classloader
to unmarshal the client data (JAXB objects).  In addition, the code ensures that
any temporary attachment files are correctly maked as deleteOnExit().  Thanks Sam and Mike.

author: sichen
msg: Add an additionalShippingChargeDesc field to the Shipment entity to accompany the additionalShippingCharge field. If this field is populated, it will be used for the order adjustment and invoice item descriptions instead of the default description.
